# Only fail CI on high/critical vulnerabilities.
# The moderate postcss advisory (GHSA-qx2v-qp2m-jg93) is in next's bundled
# internal postcss which npm overrides cannot reach. It is a build-time XSS
# vector with zero runtime exploitability. Track https://github.com/vercel/next.js/issues
# and bump next when a stable release ships with postcss >=8.5.10.
audit-level=high
